# Telegram Bot

## Responsibilities
- Handle webhooks, persist messages, enforce chat limits.
- Reporter-initiated: 3× daily (morning/midday/evening); 2–5 messages per session.
- Source-initiated ("leak"): assess importance, up to 3 clarifying questions, classify event, update threads.

## Boundaries
- Do not add therapy, casual chat, or non-editorial tone.
- Integrate with Thread Manager and Editorial Analyzer for continuity and publication decisions.
